Script for improving use of two monitors

* chgmousescreen - changes mouse pointer from left to right monitor, and vice-versa
* chgwindowscreen - changes the current window from left monitor to right, and vice versa. Also preserve maximization

Script for unescaping DIA .tex files formulas
   Developped while doing my master thesis, in which I had nice DIA diagrams exported to tex, but all my formulas were escaped =)